name: Malik REED, Petitioner v. James Murray LYNN, Respondent

parties: Malik REED, Petitioner v. James Murray LYNN, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of November, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus are GRANTED. The Court of Common Pleas of Philadelphia County is directed to dispose of Petitioner’s pending motion for credit for time served within 90 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

80 A.3d 378
Malik REED, Petitioner v. James Murray LYNN, Respondent.

Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Nov. 20, 2013.
